text:
Finally a new Malay stall in the vicinity, and just within the compound of JTC Braddell Tech industrial estate, and inside Uncle Leong Seafood coffee shop.
I have tried their nasi padang and the taste was delicious.
Most importantly the prices were very reasonable at $3.50 - $4.50.
I luv the owner she very kind and friendly and her food is tasted like a home meal food. Is not that expensive is affordable! Everyone should try it out tho !
